Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How Το Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year 1. Do a life audit Doing a life audit is crucial for pinpointing where to make adjustments and jumpstarting your new journey. Start by figuring out where you stand in the 8 areas of life health, finances, personal development, career, relationships, self-care, home life, and free time. What changes would make the biggest impact in your life for each area? @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How To Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year 2. Make a mindset shift Your mindset is what sets the tone for everything in your life. Changing your mindset is what will change your life. What we think and believe is what we act upon. Change your perspective from now on anytime anything negative happens, instead of feeling like a victim, ask yourself what you can control or change. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How To Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year 3. Create a vision Having a vision means we have a clear sense of purpose. It means we have a much larger picture of our business, or our life, than simply setting and reaching short term goals and tackling problems as they come along. Visions are driven by passion and dreams, and they are reflected through real efforts to create real results. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How Το Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year Work on yourself daily Once you have your vision, the fog lifts and your road map starts to become clear again. But, nobody is going to drive the car for you-you've got to put in the work to achieve your goals and change your own life. Consistent, daily practice is how you make that happen. If you watered the plants just a little each day, over time your garden always grew. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How To Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year 5. Design your environment for success If you want to change your life, YOU aren't the only thing that has to change-your environment has to change too. For example, if you always hang out with negative- thinking friends, you'll tend to believe the limitations they're setting for you. However, if you hang out with other "do'ers" and people who want to see you succeed, there's a much higher chance that you will. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How To Create The Life That You Want In Year 6. Learn new skills and improve upon your existing ones Nothing will change your life faster than building new skills. Whatever the case, imagine a year where you start out having a limited skill-set. Dedicate time during your day to build your skills. Learn them via books, videos, and podcasts, but don't forget to physically practice your skills too. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How Το Create The Life That You Want In Year 7. Lastly, Enjoy the process The whole point of this exercise is to CHANGE. That means your thoughts and behaviors, in addition to your surroundings, will change throughout the year. You may realize that what you initially sought isn't what you want anymore. Don't get so focused on the process that you lose sight of what YOU want and most important...having fun. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How To Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year Drop a 100 so know that you read this. This affirms that you are out achieving your goals and reaching new levels of success! 100 100 100 @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How Το Create The Life That You Want In 1 Year Thank for reading! P.S: If you're ready to start living ike and take control over your life, we've created a podcast just for the rich that. We've interviewed some of the most successful people and we're posting highly valuable content on the habits, mindsets, and patterns that create success. Click the link in the bio! @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS @AWARENESS_'.

May be an image of one or more people and text that says '5 Tips Το Be Confident From Within Have the power to change how you're feeling by controlling your body language. Physiology is key when learning how to be confident and mastering the body language of confidence can put you on the path to success. @awareness_ofsuccess'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Tips To Be Confident From Within Practice power poses Consider developing your own personal power pose and breathing deeply to reconnect to your strong core. Your pose achieves the goals of awakening your inner strength and carrying that strength and confidence into every interaction. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 15, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says '5 Tips Το Be Confident From Within Have a growth mindset. Confidence doesn't come from your outward achievements it comes from within. Being confident means that if you do fail, you can pick yourself back up and try try again. S @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Tips To Be Confident From Within Overcome your limiting benefits. Your limiting beliefs can cause you to miss out on the things that you want most. Το truly learn how to be confident, you need to believe in your capability first. Once you believe in yourself, you'll have confidence no matter what happens in life, because that confidence will come from within. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 15, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says '5 Tips Το Be Confident From Within Replacing limiting beliefs with an abundance mindset. Το overcome your self- sabotaging beliefs, put yourself in a positive mindset by making a list of things you're thankful for. Then practice flipping your limiting beliefs to empowering ones. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Unhealthy Habits That You Need Το Stop Now Not believing in yourself It's important to realize that an initial failure doesn't mean you will never be good at something. If you only stick to the first try, then you are limiting yourself to excel and grow. You can always try again and do better next time. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Unhealthy Habits That You Need Το Stop Now Not taking care of yourself You may not realize it but there is strength in taking breaks. While you're in the process of building your dreams, don't forget to take care of yourself, too. Your worth is not based on what you do, out on who you truly are. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Unhealthy Habits That You Need To Stop Now Choosing emotions over values Not being able to balance your emotions with your morals and logic is a sign of emotional weakness. How you feel should be a factor in your decisions, but when it becomes a driving force, you end up making impulsive, uninformed, and dramatic choices that you'll eventually regret. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Unhealthy Habits That You Need Το Stop Now Needing to find a reason behind everything Trying to find a reason for everything may end up making you emotionally weaker. This is because you spend more time overthinking and analyzing something you can't explain or understand. A huge sign of emotional strength iS being able to accept situations that may occur. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 Unhealthy Habits That You Need To Stop Now Trying to control everything Real freedom comes from letting go of control. To fall freely, you need to let go. If you become too set on one path, you can become close-minded and miss many opportunities simply because you're not looking anywhere else. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.
Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text.
